This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-hadoop layer.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-java
  branch: dunfell

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-hadoop layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-hadoop layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-hadoop'

II. Misc
========

meta-hadoop must be built using ipk packaging, dnf fails at do_rootfs stage 

